title: EKspresZO
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A regular Dutch lunchroom with a few choices for vegans; please inquire. Located just off the old market square. Upon request gluten free bread is available. Staff is happy to accommodate, so please ask. Very popular with lots of returning customers. Serves a range of coffees and usually has fresh mint tea. Lunch on Saturdays can be busy, so best to go early or make reservations.
